title: Female CEO’s Master - Novel Updates
author: 楚琴子
description: Chu Jiang, the leader of Mars, the top special organization in China, returned to the metropolis. In order to get a marriage contract, he entered Qingcheng Group and began his wonderful life among the flowers. Smacking the face, being a show-off and ambiguity emerged in endlessly. In the end, Chu Jiang stood at the top of the world, laughing at the world situation.>
